#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.77"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.77:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.77:0.2"
msgid "8. Arahattavagga "
msgstr "8. Perfection "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.77:0.3"
msgid "77. Uttarimanussadhammasutta "
msgstr "77. Superhuman States "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: uttari manussadhammaṃ → uttarimanussadhammā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.77:1.1"
msgid "“Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme appahāya abhabbo uttari manussadhammaṃ alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, without giving up six qualities you can’t realize a superhuman distinction in knowledge and vision worthy of the noble ones. "

msgctxt "an6.77:1.2"
msgid "Katame cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.77:1.3"
msgid "Muṭṭhassaccaṃ, asampajaññaṃ, indriyesu aguttadvārataṃ, bhojane amattaññutaṃ, kuhanaṃ, lapanaṃ. "
msgstr "Lack of mindfulness and situational awareness, not guarding the sense doors, eating too much, deceit, and flattery. "

msgctxt "an6.77:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme appahāya abhabbo uttari manussadhammaṃ alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "Without giving up these six qualities you can’t realize a superhuman distinction in knowledge and vision worthy of the noble ones. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an6.77:2.1"
msgid "Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme pahāya bhabbo uttari manussadhammaṃ alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "But after giving up six qualities you can realize a superhuman distinction in knowledge and vision worthy of the noble ones. "

msgctxt "an6.77:2.2"
msgid "Katame cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.77:2.3"
msgid "Muṭṭhassaccaṃ, asampajaññaṃ, indriyesu aguttadvārataṃ, bhojane amattaññutaṃ, kuhanaṃ, lapanaṃ. "
msgstr "Lack of mindfulness and situational awareness, not guarding the sense doors, eating too much, deceit, and flattery. "

msgctxt "an6.77:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme pahāya bhabbo uttari manussadhammaṃ alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ sacchikātun”ti. "
msgstr "After giving up these six qualities you can realize a superhuman distinction in knowledge and vision worthy of the noble ones.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.77:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

